FT  23 AUG 93 / People: P&amp;O Cruises
Mike Oldfield (above), formerly md of Sutcliffe Group Design, Sutcliffe
Healthcare Hotel Services and the South East Company, has been appointed
director hotel services at P&amp;O CRUISES. Oldfield began his career at sea
with Shaw Savill; his new remit includes hotel services on board the
Canberra and Sea Princess and the as yet unlaunched Oriana.
